item.title: CVE-2022-3596|2024-08-03T01:14:02.457Z -- red%20hat -- red%20hat%20openstack%20platform%2013.0%20-%20els
item.description: An information leak was found in OpenStack's undercloud. This flaw allows unauthenticated, remote attackers to inspect sensitive data after discovering the IP address of the undercloud, possibly leading to compromising private information, including administrator access credentials.
